   [Mesoscale Atmospheric Processes Branch Homepage]

   Mesoscale Atmospheric Processes Branch

   The mission of the Mesoscale Atmospheric Processes Branch is to
   understand the physics and dynamics of atmospheric precipitation
   systems.
